title: <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span>, <span style="color: #BFC8CC;">**DNEF**</span>에 합류
subtitle: 람바흐가 당을 전선으로 밀어 넣습니다.
view-if: chancellor = "Schleicher" and nationalists_schleicher >= 8 and dnef_formed and dnvp_leader == "Lambach"
new-page: true
